parameters:
It seems like Lunaroa's book to read before going to
sleep... It's too difficult, I don't even feel like picking
it up.
開始はティータを右側。
どこかのタイミングで左側に固定化。

\SE[15]Lady Lunaroa. I have finished taking care of the
flowers. \SE[15]They are all growing up healthy and
strong...

\SE[37]Oh no, I did it again... \SE[53]My habit of talking
to the imaginary Lady Lunaroa, which I've been doing for
three years, has completely taken root...

\SE[12]However, my mission will not change. If Lady Lunaroa
has become well, then... \SE[13]I want her to become even
more and more healthy...!

\SE[32]I need to increase my approaches...! \SE[3]Now that I
think about it, the things Lady Lunaroa would like are
probably big things, sweet things, and amazing things. I
still don't know much about them...

\SE[12]There's still room for growth, right...! \SE[13]I'm
fired up! \SE[14]I will definitely make Lady Lunaroa happy!
[3]That's the reason I live...!

\SE[37]I want to support her secretly, but I also want her
to notice me... \SE[24]One day, suddenly overwhelmed with
feelings of gratitude, while being embraced by Lady Lunaroa,
my lips...!

\SE[60]Um, I did knock just in case... \!\SE[45]But since
there was no response, I thought nobody was here...

\SE[64]I didn't see anything... \!\SE[63]I will properly
report to Mom that Tita was diligently cleaning...

\SE[1]Yes, you didn't see anything. \!\SE[3]Make sure to
properly report my efforts to Lady Lunaroa.
\!\SE[1]...Understood?

\SE[21]Mou. If you understand, then it's fine. \!\SE[0]Since
you're also part of the family, I want you to relax and
enjoy your time here.

\SE[42] (There are various people here, but this child feels
the scariest to me...)

\SE[2]Huh, what's going on today? \SE[3]Lady Lunaroa isn't
here?

\SE[0]You're helping Vita, aren't you? It looked like fun,
so I thought I'd leave you alone... \SE[63]Today, um... it's
different...

\SE[64]Because of me, Mom became bedridden... Both you and
Laura ended up feeling lonely... \SE[60]...It's all because
of my selfishness.

\SE[45]Vega...taught me. \SE[60]How difficult it is to take
care of someone who is bedridden. I think I should consider
it once too.

\SE[45]So, um... \!......\.......\!\SE[60]I'm sorry.
\!\SE[45]I thought I should apologize properly...
\SE[45] (I wonder if I'll ever be forgiven...)

\SE[2]Um, what are you apologizing for...? \SE[20]I can't
quite think of the reason...

\SE[0]I don't really understand, but... well, I got it!
\SE[0]It seems like you did something, but if you promise to
do your job properly, \SE[16]I'll apologize together with
you! As family!

\SE[4]...I got it! \SE[2] I've been wanting to express my
gratitude to you!

\SE[32]You know, I've always liked Lunaroa-sama... but...
\SE[33]I've never been able to take that one step forward.

\SE[47]I was scared of expressing my feelings and being
hated... and besides, Laura was always by your side...
\SE[48]I've always been cowardly.

\SE[14]But, now that Lunaroa-sama has become bedridden, it's
a big problem! \SE[13]I have been given the role of taking
care of you thoroughly...!

\SE[31]Happiness... I felt it... The certainty of being able
to save my beloved person... \SE[50]That emotion drove me
mad with 'love'.

\SE[0]That's why, thanks to you, I was able to take a
step forward from being a cowardly me. \SE[0]So I felt like
I had to express my gratitude.

\SE[16]Ah...! If I could say it, I would feel so relieved.
\SE[2]Well then, I'll go do the laundry. \SE[16]Even if I
feel lonely, I shouldn't sniff the scent of the bed.
\SE[16]No sniffing allowed, okay?

\SE[6]It was different from what I imagined, but... I was
able to say what I needed to say, right...?

\SE[52]Alright...! \!\SE[51]When I get back, I should
apologize to Laura too... \.It'll be fine, probably...\.I'm
sure...

\SE[69]Hang in there... me...! \!\SE[60]But, I said I hate
you.... I hope you're not angry....

\SE[0]Oh, it's already over...? \.It seems too fast
though...

\SE[3]Make sure to properly convey today's efforts to
Mom, okay? \!\SE[3]And also keep track of the growth
progress of the houseplants carefully.

\SE[16]I'm glad. I feel relieved. \SE[0]Well then, I'll go
shopping in a little while, so take care of the house, okay?
\SE[1]Oh, what kind of souvenir would you like?

\SE[62]Ch-Chocolate... \!\SE[63]If you can buy it, I don't
mind...

\SE[2]You really love him, don't you? \!\SE[16]Yes, leave it
to me.

\SE[6]That child, even though they're not angry, they're the
scariest...!!! \SE[28]Hurry back... Mom...!! I'm so scared,
I feel like I'm freezing...!

Vita hasn't completed the shitty game... but she was able to
grow a little more...!
Vita has learned the skill \i[1227] Cost-Effective Me!
